snippet.title: The First Descendant│Bunny Character Trailer
snippet.description: Have you ever met Bunny? She’s the fastest character that electrocutes enemies in the all-new looter shooter, The First Descendant. Don’t miss the chance to play as Bunny in The First Descendant’s upcoming Crossplay Open Beta that starts on September 19!
